rows.label: tlk45500152_10_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh dear, oh dear... This is a fine
pickle I've managed to wind up in.

rows.label: tlk45500152_10_msg0002
rows.name:
There was a bit of a mix-up
while I was moving some goods.

rows.label: tlk45500152_10_msg0003
rows.name:
The real precious antiques
got all in a jumble with a
bunch of counterfeits!

rows.label: tlk45500152_10_msg0004
rows.name:
Yeah, these are some really
valuable items. We're talking
around a million G.

rows.label: tlk45500152_10_msg0005
rows.name:
If I wind up giving the client a counterfeit
in place of the real thing... Let's just
say it'll be curtains for me.

rows.label: tlk45500152_10_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm clutching at straws here...
Do you know of any way to sort out
the real deal from the fakes?

rows.label: tlk45500152_10_msg0008
rows.name:
I can trust you guys with this,
right? You won't mess up, right?!
